MAGICAL OBJECTS
===============
File:          /d/Khalakhor/common/herbs/beatha.c
Creator:       Teth
Date:          January 22, 1998
Cloned by:     /d/Khalakhor/common/herbs/herb_master.c
Related Files: /d/Khalakhor/common/poisons/beathap.c
Magic prop:    ({ 85, "life" })
Other info:    This herb has a two-fold effect. It has an
               overwhelming amount of life magic, and thus
               heals living creatures upon ingestion,
               depending on a random amount added to 
               a 2x multiplier on life spells skill.
               However, to undeads, it clones a poison
               which will cause grave harm, causing reductions
               in stats, hp, and fatigue.

File:          /d/Khalakhor/inisi/roke/obj/dust.c
