Cloned by:     /d/Khalakhor/inisi/roke/npc/grugg.c
Related Files: 
Magic prop:    ({ 100, "enchantment" })
Other info:    Dust of Cold Feet. Makes it possible to walk on lava.

File:          /d/Khalakhor/inisi/roke/obj/wand.c
Creator:       Arman
Date:          February 16, 2019
Cloned by:     /d/Khalakhor/inisi/roke/npc/refnas.c
Related Files: Heal spell /d/Khalakhor/inisi/roke/obj/wand_heal_spell.c
Magic prop:    ({ 25, "enchantment" })
Other info:    Wand of Healing.

               Recoded by Arman to align with the new magic system.
               Based on the original magic wand coded by Gresolle 
               and later Glindor.

               This strange wooden stick is a wand of healing. 
               For those with spellcraft greater than 20, they 
               can hold it and use it to heal themselves or others 
               with the 'zap' command.

               The heal spell of the wand is based on the standardised 
               heal spell /d/Genesis/specials/std/spells/heal.c, with 
               a combat aid assigned to it of 35. This results in a 
               heal range of somewhere between 30 to 80 hitpoints per
               casting.

               The effectiveness of the heal is dependent on the holders 
               spellcraft skill. The wand has 10 charges, which recharge 
               at 1 charge every 30 minutes.

File:          /d/Khalakhor/inisi/roke/obj/wand.old
Creator:       Gresolle/Glindor
Date:          January 12, 2002
Cloned by:     /d/Khalakhor/inisi/roke/npc/refnas.c
Related Files: Inherits /d/Khalakhor/inisi/roke/lib/wand.c
Magic prop:    ({ 25, "enchantment" })
Other info:    Wand of Healing.
               Contains 10 charges, each healing 20+rand(40) hp.

               Obsolete and no longer in circulation. Replaced with
               /d/Khalakhor/inisi/roke/obj/wand.c

